vernac_cmds: Fixpoint subseq {A} (xs ys : list A) : Prop := match xs, ys with | [], _ => True | x :: xs', y :: ys' => (x = y /\ subseq xs' ys') \/ subseq xs ys' | _, _ => False end.
Hypothesis A_eq_dec : forall x y : A, {x = y} + {x <> y}.
Lemma subseq_refl : forall (l : list A), subseq l l.
Lemma subseq_trans : forall (zs xs ys : list A), subseq xs ys -> subseq ys zs -> subseq xs zs.
induction zs; intros; simpl in *; repeat break_match; subst; simpl in *; intuition; subst; eauto; right; (eapply IHzs; [|eauto]); simpl; eauto.
Lemma subseq_In : forall (ys xs : list A) x, subseq xs ys -> In x xs -> In x ys.
break_match; simpl in *; intuition; subst; intuition eauto; right; (eapply IHys; [eauto| intuition]).
Theorem subseq_NoDup : forall (ys xs : list A), subseq xs ys -> NoDup ys -> NoDup xs.
Lemma subseq_remove : forall (x : A) xs, subseq (remove A_eq_dec x xs) xs.
Lemma subseq_map : forall (f : A -> B) ys xs, subseq xs ys -> subseq (map f xs) (map f ys).
Lemma subseq_cons_drop : forall xs ys (a : A), subseq (a :: xs) ys -> subseq xs ys.
induction ys; intros; simpl in *; intuition; break_match; eauto.
Lemma subseq_length : forall (ys xs : list A), subseq xs ys -> length xs <= length ys.
induction ys; intros; simpl in *; break_match; intuition.
Lemma subseq_subseq_eq : forall (xs ys : list A), subseq xs ys -> subseq ys xs -> xs = ys.
induction xs; intros; destruct ys; simpl in *; intuition eauto using f_equal2, subseq_cons_drop.
Lemma subseq_filter : forall (f : A -> bool) xs, subseq (filter f xs) xs.
Lemma subseq_nil : forall xs, subseq (A:=A) [] xs.
Lemma subseq_skip : forall a xs ys, subseq(A:=A) xs ys -> subseq xs (a :: ys).
induction ys; intros; simpl in *; repeat break_match; intuition.
Lemma subseq_filterMap : forall (f : B -> option A) ys xs, subseq xs ys -> subseq (filterMap f xs) (filterMap f ys).
induction ys; intros; simpl in *; repeat break_match; auto; try discriminate; intuition; subst.
Lemma subseq_app_r : forall xs ys, subseq (A:=A) ys (xs ++ ys).
Lemma subseq_app_tail : forall ys xs zs, subseq (A:=A) xs ys -> subseq (xs ++ zs) (ys ++ zs).
Lemma subseq_app_head : forall xs ys zs, subseq (A:=A) ys zs -> subseq (A:=A) (xs ++ ys) (xs ++ zs).
Lemma subseq_2_3 : forall xs ys zs x y, subseq(A:=A) (xs ++ ys ++ zs) (xs ++ x :: ys ++ y :: zs).
Lemma subseq_middle : forall xs y zs, subseq (A:=A) (xs ++ zs) (xs ++ y :: zs).
Lemma subseq_remove_all : forall (ds l l' : list A), subseq l l' -> subseq (remove_all A_eq_dec ds l) l'.
